item.description:
@XxXB1urXxX wrote:

Ok,

1st. Get some information for a server. Like the Hamachi Network name, Hamachi pass, Port, and IP.

2nd. Go to the lil triangle on your hamachi, then “join network”, then type server info

3rd. Change the Port on Moparscape by going to “File” then “New Port”

4th. Typer your username and pass, then the server IP.

5th. Login
